ISLAMABAD, Mar 18 (APP):Federal Minister for Industries and Production, Hammad Azher said, in a tweet, that all industries, business strictly implemented Standard Operating Procedure (SOPs ) following 3rd wave of COVID-19.
“Third wave of coronavirus kicks off and adopting SOPs can save both lives and jobs,” he said.
